<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/welcome.css" />
    
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    
    <script type="importmap">
        {
        "imports": {
            "@material/web/": "https://esm.run/@material/web/"
        }
        }
    </script>
    <script type="module">
        import "@material/web/all.js";
        import { styles as typescaleStyles } from "@material/web/typography/md-typescale-styles.js";
        document.adoptedStyleSheets.push(typescaleStyles.styleSheet);
    </script>
    <script id="MathJax-script" async src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mathjax@3/es5/tex-mml-chtml.js"></script>
    </head>

<body>
    <div class="screen active" id="screen1">
        <div class="section">
            <h5 class="title">Learning by Doing</h5>
        </div>
        <div class="quiz-section">
            <img src="/images/Group 15.png" alt="Quiz">
        </div>
        <div class="container center-align" id="container">
            <div class="footer">
                <p>Learn from mistakes through hands-on practice, where active participation enhances understanding.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="screen" id="screen2">
        <div class="section">
            <h5 class="title white-text bg-red">Discovery Learning</h5>
        </div>
        <div class="hypothesis-section">
            <img src="/images/Group 16.png" alt="Dropdown">
        </div>
        <div class="container center-align" id="container">
            <div class="footer">
                <p>Discover answers with supportive guidance. Staying engaged and curious by making your own hypothesis.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="screen" id="screen3">
        <div class="section">
            <h5 class="title white-text bg-blue">Hands-on Virtual Lab</h5>
        </div>
        <div class="lab-section">
            <img src="/images/Group 17.png" alt="Virtual Lab">
        </div>
        <div class="container center-align" id="container">
            <div class="footer">
                <p>Explore the exciting world of hands-on virtual labs, where learning becomes an immersive adventure!</p>
            </div>
        </div>   
    </div>

    <div class="screen" id="screen4">

        <div class="header">
            <div class="header-content">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined close-icon" onclick="goBack()">close</span>
              <h1>Course Overview</h1>
            </div>
        </div>
      
        <div class="instruction-content">
            <h2>Topic: The Figure of Merit of Galvanometer</h2>
            <p>This course integrates evidence-based learning strategies to deepen your understanding of the figure of merit of galvanometer lab experiment.</p>
            <div class="tags">
                <span>Hands-on Learning</span>
                <span>Practical Exam</span>
                <span>Galvanometer</span>
                <span>Physics Lab</span>
            </div>
            <div class="expectations">
                <h2>What's To Expect?</h2>
                <div class="time">
                    <img src="/images/Clock.png" alt="Time">
                    <p><b>Time:</b> 1.5 hours</p>
                </div>
                <div class="format">
                    <img src="/images/Read.png" alt="Format">
                    <p><b>Format:</b> Learning by doing</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="button-container">
                <md-filled-button class="start-button" data-key="next_section_principle">I'm Ready</md-filled-button>
            </div>
        </div>
        
    </div>

    <div class="container center-align" id="container">
        <nav class="navigation">
            <div class="dot" onclick="showScreen(1)"></div>
            <div class="dot" onclick="showScreen(2)"></div>
            <div class="dot" onclick="showScreen(3)"></div>
            <div class="dot" onclick="showScreen(4)"></div>
        </nav>
    </div>

    <script src="/javascript/welcome.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
